- Idea 1 advances this into a *dynamic, sequential* framework that models transitions across multiple turns, simulating how answerability degrades over time via role disruptions. It introduces a Role Transition Network (RTN) and a "role flow loss" to track evolution of span validity—a significantly more complex and cognitively grounded process.

